text: Ferenc Tóth (30 December 1950 – 4 December 2020) was a Hungarian engineer and Fidesz politician. He was a member of the National Assembly (MP) for Paks (Tolna County Constituency II) between 1998 and 2014. Tóth died on 4 December 2020 from COVID-19, aged 70. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Hungarian politicians Category:Hungarian engineers Category:Hungarian businesspeople Category:Deaths from the COVID-19 pandemic in Hungary Category:Tolna County
